<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>NPO法人やまぼうしネットワーク | 認知症になっても暮らしやすい社会へ</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --orange: #E8853A;
    --orange-light: #F5A96B;
    --orange-pale: #FDF0E6;
    --orange-deep: #C4631A;
    --green: #4A7C59;
    --green-light: #EBF3EE;
    --warm-white: #FDFAF6;
    --off-white: #F7F3ED;
    --text-dark: #2A2118;
    --text-mid: #5C4A38;
    --text-light: #9C8070;
    --border: rgba(90,60,30,0.12);
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    background: var(--warm-white);
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(253,250,246,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 5%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    height: 68px;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-logo-mark {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    background: var(--orange);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;
    color: white; letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .nav-logo-text { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-dark); line-height: 1.4; }
  .nav-logo-text span { display: block; font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-light); font-weight: 400; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-mid); transition: color 0.2s; font-weight: 500; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--orange); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--orange); color: white;
    border: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 24px;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--orange-deep); }
  .nav-mobile-toggle { display: none; }

  /* HERO */
  #hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FDF0E6 0%, #F7F3ED 60%, #EBF3EE 100%);
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .hero-pattern {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0; opacity: 0.04;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle, #C4631A 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 28px 28px;
  }
  .hero-circle-deco { display: none; }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 600px; padding: 120px 0 80px 8%; }
  .hero-photo-col {
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    height: 100vh; min-height: 600px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-photo-col img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
  }
  .hero-photo-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(253,240,230,0.35) 0%, transparent 40%);
  }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 24px; padding: 6px 16px;
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-mid); margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .hero-badge-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--orange); }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .hero-title em { color: var(--orange); font-style: normal; }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-mid);
    margin-bottom: 40px; line-height: 1.9; max-width: 500px;
  }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--orange); color: white;
    padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 32px;
    text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px;
    transition: all 0.2s; display: inline-block;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--orange-deep); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(200,90,30,0.3); }
  .btn-outline {
    border: 1.5px solid var(--text-mid); color: var(--text-mid);
    padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 32px;
    text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 15px;
    transition: all 0.2s; display: inline-block;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--orange); color: var(--orange); }
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex; gap: 40px; margin-top: 56px;
    padding-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .stat-item { }
  .stat-num { font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--orange); line-height: 1; }
  .stat-unit { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-light); }
  .stat-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-light); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* SECTION BASE */
  section { padding: 96px 5%; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--orange); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 38px);
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-dark);
    line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .section-desc { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-mid); max-width: 540px; line-height: 1.9; }
  .section-header { margin-bottom: 56px; }

  /* ABOUT */
  #about { background: white; }
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center; }
  .about-visual {
    position: relative; aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    background: var(--orange-pale);
    border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .photo-slider {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; position: relative;
  }
  .photo-slide {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.8s ease;
  }
  .photo-slide.active { opacity: 1; }
  .photo-slide img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  .photo-caption {
    position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(30,15,5,0.65));
    color: white; font-size: 12px; padding: 32px 16px 12px;
    border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .photo-dots {
    position: absolute; bottom: 12px; right: 14px;
    display: flex; gap: 6px; z-index: 2;
  }
  .photo-dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .photo-dot.active { background: white; }
  .about-quote {
    position: absolute; bottom: -20px; right: -20px;
    background: white; border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 20px 24px; max-width: 240px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .about-quote p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.7; }
  .about-quote-author { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-light); margin-top: 8px; font-weight: 500; }
  .about-text p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .about-award {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    background: var(--orange-pale); border: 1px solid rgba(230,130,60,0.3);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 20px; margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .award-icon { font-size: 24px; }
  .award-text { font-size: 13px; color: var(--orange-deep); font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ACTIVITIES */
  #activities { background: var(--off-white); }
  .activities-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .activity-card {
    background: white; border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 36px 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .activity-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .activity-card::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px;
    background: var(--orange);
    transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .activity-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .activity-icon {
    width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--orange-pale);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 26px;
  }
  .activity-card h3 { font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .activity-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.8; }
  .activity-tag {
    display: inline-block; margin-top: 16px;
    background: var(--orange-pale); color: var(--orange-deep);
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px;
  }

  /* NEWS */
  #news { background: white; }
  .news-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: start; }
  .news-list { }
  .news-item {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; gap: 20px;
    padding: 24px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .news-item:hover { opacity: 0.7; }
  .news-item:first-child { padding-top: 0; }
  .news-date { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-light); padding-top: 4px; font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; }
  .news-cat { font-size: 11px; color: var(--orange); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .news-item-title { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dark); font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.7; }
  .news-highlight {
    background: var(--orange-pale); border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(230,130,60,0.2);
  }
  .news-highlight-label { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--orange); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .news-highlight h3 { font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--text-dark); line-height: 1.5; }
  .news-highlight p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .news-highlight a { font-size: 13px; color: var(--orange); font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }
  .news-highlight a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  /* SUPPORT */
  #support { background: var(--off-white); }
  .support-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .support-card {
    background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px 28px;
    text-align: center; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  .support-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .support-card.featured {
    background: var(--orange); border-color: var(--orange);
  }
  .support-card.featured * { color: white !important; }
  .support-card.featured .support-btn { background: white; color: var(--orange) !important; }
  .support-card.featured .support-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); }
  .support-icon { font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 16px; display: block; }
  .support-card h3 { font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .support-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .support-btn {
    display: inline-block; background: var(--orange); color: white;
    padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 24px; text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .support-btn:hover { background: var(--orange-deep); }

  /* CONTACT */
  #contact { background: white; }
  .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; }
  .contact-info h2 { font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--text-dark); }
  .contact-info p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .contact-detail { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .contact-item { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .contact-item-icon {
    width: 40px; height: 40px; min-width: 40px;
    background: var(--orange-pale); border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 18px;
  }
  .contact-item-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.7; }
  .contact-item-text strong { display: block; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-light); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .contact-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .form-group label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-mid); font-weight: 500; display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .form-group input,
  .form-group textarea,
  .form-group select {
    width: 100%; padding: 14px 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--warm-white); color: var(--text-dark);
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif; font-size: 15px;
    outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s;
    appearance: none;
  }
  .form-group input:focus,
  .form-group textarea:focus,
  .form-group select:focus { border-color: var(--orange); }
  .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 120px; }
  .form-submit {
    background: var(--orange); color: white;
    border: none; padding: 16px; border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    transition: background 0.2s; width: 100%;
  }
  .form-submit:hover { background: var(--orange-deep); }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--text-dark); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    padding: 64px 5% 36px;
  }
  .footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .footer-brand { }
  .footer-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .footer-logo-mark {
    width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--orange); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: white;
  }
  .footer-logo-text { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: white; }
  .footer-brand p { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 280px; }
  .footer-section h4 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .footer-links { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .footer-links a { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--orange-light); }
  .footer-bottom {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding-top: 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .footer-bottom p { font-size: 12px; }
  .footer-sns { display: flex; gap: 12px; }
  .sns-btn {
    width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    text-decoration: none; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 14px; transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .sns-btn:hover { background: var(--orange); color: white; }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .fade-up { animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards; opacity: 0; }
  .delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .delay-3 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .delay-4 { animation-delay: 0.4s; }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    #hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-photo-col { height: 52vw; min-height: 260px; }
    .hero-content { padding: 100px 6% 40px; }
    .about-grid, .news-layout, .contact-grid, .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .activities-grid, .support-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .nav-links, .nav-cta { display: none; }
    .nav-mobile-toggle { display: block; font-size: 24px; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-dark); }
    .about-quote { position: static; margin-top: 20px; max-width: 100%; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .activities-grid, .support-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    section { padding: 64px 5%; }
    .hero-stats { gap: 24px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAVIGATION -->
<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">
    <div class="nav-logo-mark">や</div>
    <div class="nav-logo-text">
      NPO法人やまぼうしネットワーク
      <span>認知症になっても暮らしやすい社会へ</span>
    </div>
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">私たちについて</a></li>
    <li><a href="#activities">活動内容</a></li>
    <li><a href="#news">お知らせ</a></li>
    <li><a href="#support">支援する</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">お問い合わせ</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#support" class="nav-cta">ご支援・寄付</a>
  <button class="nav-mobile-toggle">☰</button>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-pattern"></div>
  <div class="hero-circle-deco"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge fade-up">
      <span class="hero-badge-dot"></span>
      岩手県滝沢市を拠点に活動中
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title fade-up delay-1">
      <em>認知症になっても</em><br>
      自分らしく、<br>
      暮らせるまちへ。
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub fade-up delay-2">
      スローショッピングをはじめ、認知症のある方とその家族が安心して地域で暮らし続けられる社会をつくるための活動をしています。
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions fade-up delay-3">
      <a href="#activities" class="btn-primary">活動を見る</a>
      <a href="#support" class="btn-outline">支援・寄付する</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats fade-up delay-4">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">200<span class="stat-unit" style="font-size:18px;">回+</span></div>
        <div class="stat-label">スローショッピング開催実績</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">4,000<span class="stat-unit" style="font-size:18px;">人+</span></div>
        <div class="stat-label">延べ参加者数</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">2019</div>
        <div class="stat-label">活動開始年</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-photo-col">
    <img src="https://theotol.soudan-e65.com/assets/slow_shopping_vol1_279d45c99b.jpg" alt="スローショッピングの様子 マイヤ滝沢店" onerror="this.src='https://theotol.soudan-e65.com/assets/slow_shopping_vol1_47f3a4adaa.jpg'">
    <div class="hero-photo-overlay"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-visual">
      <div class="photo-slider" id="photoSlider">
        <div class="photo-slide active">
          <img src="https://theotol.soudan-e65.com/assets/slow_shopping_vol1_01_a97b758b73.jpg"
               alt="パートナーと一緒に売り場を歩く様子"
               onerror="this.style.display='none'">
          <div class="photo-caption">パートナーが寄り添い、本人のペースで売り場を巡る（マイヤ滝沢店）</div>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-slide">
          <img src="https://theotol.soudan-e65.com/assets/slow_shopping_vol2_6f7258df6f_318b6de5e9_49f5a92c15.webp"
               alt="スローショッピングの様子 vol2"
               onerror="this.style.display='none'">
          <div class="photo-caption">毎週木曜日、マイヤ滝沢店で開催中のスローショッピング</div>
